h3. Steps to reproduce

# Click page create button, then select 'Decision' blueprint.
# Enter Decision entry.
# Enter any non-ascii character(s) in Background entry of the Decision blueprint wizard.
# Clink create button.

h3. Examples

Entered text in the wizard is:
{noformat}
あいうえお
かきくけこ
{noformat}

Text in the created page is:
{noformat}
&#12354;&#12356;&#12358;&#12360;&#12362; 
&#12363;&#12365;&#12367;&#12369;&#12371; 
{noformat}

Best regards,
Kan Ogawa

h3. Fix
Upgrade the Business Blueprints Pack Plugin to 1.7.4 or above. The download is available from the [Atlassian Marketplace|https://marketplace.atlassian.com/plugins/com.atlassian.confluence.plugins.confluence-business-blueprints].

